paragraph.text:
A Public Water System, as such term is defined by 
              section 1401 of the Safe Drinking Water Act (
              Public Law 93–523
            ; 
              42 U.S.C. 300f
            ).

A Treatment Works, as such term is defined in 
              section 212 of the Federal Water Pollution Control Act (
              Public Law 92–500
            ; 
              33 U.S.C. 12920
            ).
